# ============================================================
#  AI Video Generation — Environment Config (optional)
# ============================================================
#
#  Copy this file to .env and uncomment lines you want to override.
#  In most cases you do NOT need to change anything — all paths
#  are automatically resolved relative to the repo directory.
#
# ── Server ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PORT=7860
#
# ── Device override (auto-detected if not set) ───────────────
# Force CPU even if CUDA is available:
# FORCE_CPU=1
#
# ── Notes ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  - Models are cached in:  <repo>/models/hf_cache/
#  - T2M-GPT lives in:      <repo>/t2m_gpt/
#  - Generated videos in:   <repo>/outputs/
#  - Server logs in:        <repo>/logs/
#  - Nothing is written outside the repo directory.
